    <published>2023-09-22T16:00:06.000Z</published>
    <updated>2023-09-22T16:03:01.038Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://copy-alcide.github.io/post-images/MMDPic-2023/Aya_20230923.png&default=https://copy-alcide.github.io/post-images/MMDPic-2023/Aya_20230923.png"></p><p>第一次在學校中做 MMD，也許也算是一種新的開始吧。</p><p>一直沒太搞明白眼鏡的玻璃材質該怎麽處理比較好，目前還是先用這種方案。</p><span id="more"></span><figure class="highlight plaintext"><figcaption><span>Text</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">借物表</span><br><span class="line">模型：</span><br><span class="line">宝改 MikuMikuDance用　東方Project　射命丸文改変モデル</span><br><span class="line">モノゾフ モブメガネ2</span><br><span class="line">ところてん36 MikuMikuDance用モデル：万年筆と小物セット</span><br><span class="line">Zippo 文庫本と新書本のセット</span><br><span class="line">ケロリン町3.0 for MMDセット BTA(Kelorin Jo)</span><br><span class="line">渲染：</span><br><span class="line">Rui Ray-MMD</span><br><span class="line">極北P dPostPointLight_v1.00</span><br><span class="line">そぼろ 面光源エフェクト PanelLight</span><br><span class="line">ikeno ikBokeh_v020a</span><br><span class="line">そぼろ MikuMikuEffect用ディフュージョンフィルタ</span><br><span class="line">RedialC Toon_RC</span><br><span class="line">世界最弱のサーモントラウト RayMMD用のマテリアル24種類</span><br><span class="line">ビームマンP 多光源エフェクト</span><br><span class="line">軟件：</span><br><span class="line">MMM ver 1.2.9.2</span><br><span class="line">MMD ver 9.26</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://copy-alcide.github.io/post-images/MMDPic-2023/Aya_20230923.png&amp;default=https://copy-alcide.github.io/post-images/MMDPic-2023/Aya_20230923.png&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;第一次在學校中做 MMD，也許也算是一種新的開始吧。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;一直沒太搞明白眼鏡的玻璃材質該怎麽處理比較好，目前還是先用這種方案。&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
